son\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>, then <span aria-label=\"f\"><math alttext=\"f\"><semantics><mi>f</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span> is an even function.</p>","<p class=\"dap_body\">​If <span aria-label=\"c equals 2 pi\"><math alttext=\"c equals 2 pi\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>, then <span aria-label=\"f\"><math alttext=\"f\"><semantics><mi>f</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span> is an even function.​</p>","<p class=\"dap_body\">​There is no value of <span aria-label=\"c\"><math alttext=\"c\"><semantics><mi>c</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span> for which <span aria-label=\"f\"><math alttext=\"f\"><semantics><mi>f</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span> is an even function.​</p>"],"answer":"B-21590"}]